{"tid":810604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日老母係我臉前倒曬啲湯落地下","createTime":"2018-09-08T06:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T16:37:48.000Z","uid":54581,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"54fda27c8306d5a53e3ec574b753cbfa9ba4729d","tid":810604,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"話說陳晚我放工煲湯<br />\n煲起滾晒緊係拿拿聲拎俾老母飲<br />\n點知佢話睇緊延希分唔到神飲 話一陣飲<br />\n點知佢睇完一集接一集都唔飲 咪入去提佢飲<br />\n最後佢睇到唔知邊鳩個俾雷劈死就發脾氣<br />\n係我臉前倒晒碗湯落地下<br />\n我真係嬲到流左兩滴眼淚再死狗咁拖番塊地<br />\n我心諗你一開始飲左佢咪得囉話晒放工都煲湯你飲 想你飲碗熱湯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4631af653c4b1e2f820ff732853dbd0e7099dc7b","tid":810604,"uid":80982,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"伯母好波"},{"pid":"a1c8f8916ca161227d901a11ed93662038d65b38","tid":810604,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351469af4cecda75f0ffd0f6fb142c3bee824e9c","tid":810604,"uid":27443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3bb109415d40bb541fec33860404e67cb3dce1","tid":810604,"uid":149852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"做咩唔打伯友"},{"pid":"dc4ffe1928d7ea7ba284b664b73ed03135acbd49","tid":810604,"uid":59678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"伯友ho ball"},{"pid":"5bc2220d178d9a6df9fcaabbe3f6094e6f512c7c","tid":810604,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"你煲啲雞翼魚蛋湯點飲呀"},{"pid":"befeeb71d0180697c35a79b2404d945915ae4a91","tid":810604,"uid":153279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:22:10.